      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. Under the hood, the S54B32 straight-six remains a mechanical masterpiece, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system, delivering a linear power curve up to its 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis is impeccably maintained, with recent preventative subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement fully documented. Finished in original Carbon Black metallic, the exterior retains a factory-fresh luster, while the interior shows zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key, investment-quality icon for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
