    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like luster and zero rock chips or blemishes. The interior is equally pristine, retaining its original factory leather scent with absolutely no wear on the bolsters, carpets, or touchpoints. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the climate control, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been strictly garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized centers with a comprehensive maintenance log included. It delivers a driving experience that is as tight and responsive as the day it was first delivered. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this is an unparalleled opportunity.",
